    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>I have a <span class="caps">BIT</span>, <span class="caps">MIT</span> and PhD in computer science. My PhD is about search spaces, filesystems, and finite lattices. In simple terms &#8212; desktop search that doesn&#8217;t suck.</p>
<p>I have presented libferris at <span class="caps">LCA</span> 2002, the Linux Kongress 2005 &amp; 08, <span class="caps">OLS</span> 2007, <span class="caps">NLUUG</span> storage conference 2009, <span class="caps">UKUUG</span> spring conference 2010, and others.</p>
